// Exercise: Closure-based secret keeper
// 1. Write a function 'createVault' that takes a secret string
// 2. Return an object with:
//    - verify(guess): returns 'Correct!' if guess === secret,
//      otherwise 'Wrong!'
//    - hint(): returns `Starts with '${first}' and ends with '${last}'`
//      where first and last are the first and last characters of the secret
